\par Father\rquote s family\rquote s money came from a department store in Plymouth. Paternal grandfather did all the legal work for the firm \endash  which was sold to Debenhams in the 1930s \endash  and then beca
me a gentleman farmer. Paternal grandmother conventional daughter of minor landed gentry from Dorset. 
\par Saw both sets of grandparents during the summer. Mother didn\rquote t get on with her paternal grandmother. 
